a s\\u00e9ria, moderna e comprometida com o conceito da avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva, que encurta&nbsp;dist\\u00e2ncias sem abrir m\\u00e3o da qualidade, seguran\\u00e7a e conforto.&nbsp;<\\/span>\",\"historia_texto_en\":\"SyncJet was founded in 2013 with the purpose of making business aviation accessible and efficient. Throughout time, we increased the number of airplanes in our management program, as well as the number of crew members and employees, to meet our mission of offering high-quality business aviation services.<br \\/>\\r\\nThe initiatives of partners Liston and Pedro resulted in a serious and modern company, dedicated to the concept of business aviation that shortens distances without giving up on quality, safety, and comfort.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\"historia_texto_es\":\"\",\"imagem_texto\":\"historia_next.png\",\"frase_inauguracao\":\"Dia da inaugura\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Janeiro de 2014.\",\"frase_inauguracao_en\":\"\",\"frase_inauguracao_es\":\"\",\"texto_visao\":\"Oferecer servi\\u00e7os diferenciados e de alta qualidade para usu\\u00e1rios da avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva, com conforto, seguran\\u00e7a e pontualidade.\",\"texto_visao_en\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Offering unique, high-quality services for business aviation users, with comfort, safety, and punctuality.<\\/span>\",\"texto_visao_es\":\"\",\"texto_missao\":\"Ser uma empresa reconhecida mundialmente por tornar a avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o simples, eficaz e acess\\u00edvel, expandindo o acesso a avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva.\",\"texto_missao_en\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Being a company recognized worldwide for providing streamlined, efficient, and accessible aviation, expanding the access to business aviation.<\\/span>\",\"texto_missao_es\":\"\",\"texto_valores\":\"\\u00c9tica, Inova\\u00e7\\u00e3o, Qualidade, Transpar\\u00eancia, Credibilidade e Comprometimento.\",\"texto_valores_en\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Ethic, Innovation, Quality, Transparency, Credib