practicality with the seriousness the business aviation requires. Know the SyncJet way of managing aircraft. \",\"frase_banner_es\":\"\",\"texto1\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">A SyncJet \\u00e9 uma empresa focada na avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva descomplicada. Gra\\u00e7as \\u00e0 experi\\u00eancia dos gestores, a SyncJet desenvolve um trabalho compromissado, inteligente e s\\u00e9rio no ramo da avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva, agilizando a vida de quem n\\u00e3o pode perder tempo com burocracia e precisa de facilidade para honrar com os compromissos.<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nDesde 2013, o trabalho \\u00e9 realizado seguindo rigorosamente todos os protocolos de seguran\\u00e7a que a avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva exige, al\\u00e9m de possuir uma frota moderna com as aeronaves mais conceituadas do mercado.&nbsp;<\\/span>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Os servi\\u00e7os da SyncJet focam na propriedade compartilhada de aeronaves, t\\u00e1xi a\\u00e9reo e gest\\u00e3o de aeronaves, sempre com muita responsabilidade e cuidado sem complica\\u00e7\\u00f5es.&nbsp;A nossa gest\\u00e3o inteligente cumpre com a miss\\u00e3o de oferecer servi\\u00e7os de alta qualidade do jeito que os nossos clientes exigem.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"texto1_en\":\"SyncJet is a company focused on hassle-free business aviation. Thanks to the experience of its managers, SyncJet develops loyal, smart, and serious work in the business aviation field, speeding the life of those who cannot waste time with bureaucracy and need easy processes to meet their own commitments.<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nSince 2013, we&rsquo;ve been developing our work strictly following all safety protocols the business aviation requires, as well as having a modern fleet with the most reputed aircraft in the market.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nSyncJet services focus on shared ownership of aircraft, Charter, and aircraft management, always with great responsibility and care, free of complications.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\"texto1_es\":\"\",\"texto2\":\"SyncJet focada na avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva descomplicada.\",\"texto2_en\":\"SyncJet focused on uncomplicated business aviation.\",\"texto2_es\":null,\"historia_texto\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">A SyncJet nasceu em 2013 com o objetivo de tornar a avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva acess\\u00edvel e eficaz. Ao longo do tempo, aumentamos o n\\u00famero de aeronaves em nosso programa de gest\\u00e3o, de tripulantes e colaboradores, que cumprem a miss\\u00e3o de oferecer servi\\u00e7os de avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva de alta qualidade.<br \\/>\\r\\nA iniciativas dos s\\u00f3cios Liston e Pedro resultou em uma empresa s\\u00e9ria, moderna e comprometida com o conceito da avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva, que encurta&nbsp;dist\\u00e2ncias sem abrir m\\u00e3o da qualidade, seguran\\u00e7a e conforto.&nbsp;<\\/span>\",\"historia_texto_en\":\"SyncJet was founded in 2013 with the purpose of making business aviation accessible and efficient. Throughout time, we increased the number of airplanes in our management program, as well as the number of crew members and employees, to meet our mission of offering high-quality business aviation services.<br \\/>\\r\\nThe initiatives of partners Liston and Pedro resulted in a serious and modern company, dedicated to the concept of business aviation that shortens distances without giving up on quality, safety, and comfort.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\"historia_texto_es\":\"\",\"imagem_texto\":\"historia_next.png\",\"frase_inauguracao\":\"Dia da inaugura\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Janeiro de 2014.\",\"frase_inauguracao_en\":\"Opening - January 2014.\",\"frase_inauguracao_es\":\"\",\"texto_visao\":\"Oferecer servi\\u00e7os diferenciados e de alta qualidade para usu\\u00e1rios da avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva, com conforto, seguran\\u00e7a e pontualidade.\",\"texto_visao_en\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Offering unique, high-quality services for business aviation users, with comfort, safety, and punctuality.<\\/span>\",\"texto_visao_es\":\"\",\"texto_missao\":\"Ser uma empresa reconhecida mundialmente por tornar a avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o simples, eficaz e acess\\u00edvel, expandindo o acesso a avia\\u00e7\\u00e3o executiva.\",\"texto_missao_en\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Being a company recognized worldwide for providing streamlined, efficient, and accessible aviation, expanding the access to business aviation.<\\/span>\",\"texto_missao_es\":\"\",\"texto_valores\":\"\\u00c9tica, Inova\\u00e7\\u00e3o, Qualidade, Transpar\\u00eancia, Credibilidade e Comprometimento.\",\"texto_valores_en\":\"<span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Ethic, Innovation, Quality, Transparency, Credibility, and Commitment.<\\/span>\",\"texto_valores_es\":\"\",\"comoatendemos_imagem\":\"como_atendemos.jpg\",\"comoatendemos_titulo_imagem\":\"Organograma de atendimento\",\"comoatendemos_titulo_imagem_en\":\"Service organization chart\",\"comoatendemos_titulo_imagem_es\":\"\",\"comoatendemos_texto\":\"Dedica\\u00e7\\u00e3o TOTAL. Criamos identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o com nosso target, envolvendo nossos servi\\u00e7os e seus benef\\u00edcios em temas relevantes para nossos clientes, como business, viagens, lazer e fam\\u00edlia, oferencendo um servi\\u00e7o personalizado e que atende as necessidades espec\\u00edficas de cada perfil.\",\"comoatendemos_texto_en\":\"TOTAL dedication. We create identification with our target, involving our services and their benefits in topics relevant to our customers, such as business, travel, leisure and family, offering a personalized service that meets the specific needs of each profile.\",\"comoatendemos_texto_es\":\"\",\"home_link_video\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=WxILLduscS8\",\"home_capa_video\":\"aad3a1a6e3bf693d5ea3d82ad5ab097c.png\"}',_binary '{\"banner_home_desktop\":\"\"}','UPDATE','\"Mozilla\\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\\/122.0.0.0 Safari\\/537.36\"','2024-03-03 20: